{"type": "article", "id": 12319, "title": "气氛之灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-20T08:13:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135609xVsHPgiWbZfUQ0zn.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>来自荷兰埃因霍温的设计师 Daan Spanjers 把时间的流逝和光影的变化结合在一起，设计了一款叫做 “Atmosphere” 的光谱时钟。选定基调后，从日出到日落，时间的变化，不同的湿度和地理位置，摆放角度的变化都会使得时钟的颜色随之改变，让你拥有独特的日出和日落。但是，既然名为“气氛”，那么你也别指望它能指示你精确的时间，它更多的作用还是在于让你的一面小墙壁甚至一个房间，变得更浪漫有趣一点。<a href=\"http://daanspanjers.nl/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看设计师的个人主页。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140059qd28JrfeVLGUak7T.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1065\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140100IvxQtXRTyr190gAh.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1065\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261401005kwSiNdATUGmb0uZ.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1065\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140101jPcdnF8alfeh9iux.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1065\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140102QABG5lKy1oeOgntr.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1065\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140102YznPEdDIJAHMexpy.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"1065\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img sr